    "description": "The \"Grim Reaper\" of the battlefield returns to his middle school days. Kurona Masamune, a mercenary who single-handedly turns the tide of battle on the East African battlefield, faithfully followed his father's teachings: \"Don't have your own will, just follow orders.\" Living as the ultimate \"tool,\" he loses his life due to betrayal during a mission. However, when he awakens, he finds himself in a middle school classroom 15 years in the past. \"If I could do it over, I could do it better...\" With this dying regret in his heart, the strongest former mercenary crushes evil within the school with \"his own will\" in this revenge action!\n\nSource: [eBookJapan](https://ebookjapan.yahoo.co.jp/books/986099/?type=serialStory), Translated",
